OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FBT to cut up to 55,000 jobs
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Fby end of decade           
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5F                           
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, Telecoms giant BT is to cut up to      
OL,6, 55,000 jobs by the end of the decade as
OL,7, it seeks to cut costs.                 
OL,9,FThe headcount reduction, which will be 
OL,10,Fup to 40% of employees, is out of a    
OL,11,Fcurrent workforce of 130,000.          
OL,13,FChief executive Philip Jansen said that
OL,14,Fby the end of the 2020s BT will have a 
OL,15,F"much smaller workforce" and a         
OL,16,F"significantly reduced cost base".     
OL,18,FThe announcement was made as BT        
OL,19,Freported a 12% drop in profits of      
OL,20,F#1.7bn for the year to April.          
